title: Jimmy Neutron (2002-2005) TV all shows new DVD rip
description:
The great Nickelodeon TV series "The Adventures of Jimmy Neutron: Boy Genius", in a new rip of the full 10-DVD set. 

Published 2014 in Germany, this is the only complete commercial edition. It has English and German audio tracks, with German episode menus. The full booklet is included with all the episode titles in English as well. 

No more fuzzy TV downloads! These are the full original 7GB DVDs (no further compression) of this brilliantly written animated series. Fun for adults as well as kids, it will be a classic through time
